{"tid":541381,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［bio撚入］點樣從激素同身體徵狀分析月經週期？","createTime":"2018-01-26T11:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T13:38:01.000Z","uid":82143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d47dde0e2f69e3161590b37d571cbc25cdaf0529","tid":541381,"uid":82143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T11:05:23.000Z","msg":"即係好似一個女仔<br />\n如果黎m前 即係排卵後 通常有機會皮膚差（雌激素降低）<br />\n咁假設男女行房完<br />\n佢又係排卵後有皮膚差既徵狀<br />\n咁係咪代表佢一定將會有月經？<br />\n係排卵之後 身體徵狀有咩明顯變化先會知道女方將會有月經發生（根據激素既分泌/抑制推論）"},{"pid":"541690de879f18dd9dec1d49cdd5bd9177feb28e","tid":541381,"uid":82143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T11:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc17b37a4817f66c15f1ac00e36065204bb009be","tid":541381,"uid":141435,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T11:16:29.000Z","msg":"問連登班毒撚小學雞識閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc4da9527d009c88da953d4c8c69f5f18bc321e","tid":541381,"uid":82143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc17b37a4817f66c15f1ac00e36065204bb009be","tid":541381,"uid":141435,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T11:16:29.000Z","msg":"問連登班毒撚小學雞識閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"巴打我明你意思<br />\n但除左咁我仲想知<br />\n到底呢種經前特徵<br />\n會唔會同樣出現係即將有左既女仔身上？<br />\n即係有晒以前種種經前徵兆 臨尾都係有bb<br />\n我讀得書少諗唔明會唔會咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118fbbd2b7a463496c7ecfe8e3ddf1f9cf8101b7","tid":541381,"uid":141435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"Btw ching如果中出咗又淆底嘅買事後好過上連登斷鳩估啦。<br />\n<br />\n爸爸咗就喊都冇謂"},{"pid":"9cbf6a0